name: Putt Putt GO! (for the Oculus Go)
name_original: Putt Putt GO! (for the Oculus Go)
description:
A wacky putt putt golf game for the Oculus Go.

Set in a world where putt putt golf is celebrated as a major sport, excite the crowd with your world class skills!

Features:

  • Three unique levels to complete
  • High score leader board - Compete with your friends!
  • Collectibles scattered throughout every level
  • Three different clubs!

Developed in three weeks by:

  • Dylan Clarke - Level Design & Sound
  • Adam Klappers - Project Management & Design
  • James Brown - Physics and Programming
  • Jordan Sangster-Williams  - Physics and Programming
  • Byron Boskell - Scoring and Programming
  • D'arcy Knock - Game Art
  • Hudson Liebelt - Game Art

Made at the Academy of Interactive Entertainment Adelaide

Thank you for playing!
